text: Jacoba Wijnands (28 June 1924 - 2 February 2019) was a Dutch gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Dutch female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the Netherlands Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Rotterdam
